OL,3,CContractor appointed to complete
OL,4,CBerwick community hospital
OL,6,FA permanent contractor has been
OL,7,Fappointed to finish building a
OL,8,Fcommunity hospital in Berwick.
OL,10,FGateshead-based Robertson Construction
OL,11,FNorth East will take over the project,
OL,12,Fwith the goal of having the site ready
OL,13,Fto open in spring 2027.
OL,15,FConstruction on the hospital began in
OL,16,F2023 but stopped in November 2025 when
OL,17,Fthe previous contractor Merit
OL,18,FConstruction went into administration.
