OL,3,CContractor appointed to complete
OL,4,CBerwick community hospital
OL,6,FWork restarted in December under an
OL,7,Finterim contractor and Robertson
OL,8,FConstruction will take over management
OL,9,Fof the site in the mid-February, with
OL,10,Fa timeline for completion expected at
OL,11,Fthe end of the month.
OL,13,FThe firm previously built the
OL,14,FCommunity Diagnostic Centre at the
OL,15,FMetrocentre and the new Urgent
OL,16,FTreatment Centre at the Royal Victoria
OL,17,FInfirmary in Newcastle.
