OL,3,CContractor appointed to complete
OL,4,CBerwick community hospital
OL,6,FDamon Kent, managing director of
OL,7,FNorthumbria Healthcare Facilities
OL,8,FManagement said: "The last few months
OL,9,Fhave been difficult for many, and we
OL,10,Fappreciate the concern surrounding the
OL,11,Fconstruction of what is such a vital
OL,12,Fhealthcare facility for Berwick and
OL,13,Fthe surrounding areas.
OL,15,F"We are very pleased that we can now
OL,16,Fmove forward with the appointment of
OL,17,FRobertson Construction North East and
OL,18,Fthat they are committed to working
OL,19,Fwith previous sub-contractors and
OL,20,Fsuppliers.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
