OL,3,CContractor appointed to complete
OL,4,CBerwick community hospital
OL,6,F"I know that people are keen to
OL,7,Funderstand when our colleagues and
OL,8,Fpatients will be able to access our
OL,9,Fnew Berwick hospital.
OL,11,F"It is difficult at this stage to give
OL,12,Fan exact timeframe, but we are hoping
OL,13,Fthe hospital will open by spring 2027.
OL,14,FWe thank everyone for their continued
OL,15,Fpatience and understanding."
